nodes.text: Opop Hibbedit was an astronomical object covered in forests and jungles. During the second year of the Clone Wars, a squad of B1-series battle droids, including Q5-7070, was sent to survey Opop Hibbedit.

Opop Hibbedit was a remote astronomical object located covered by forests, jungles, and mud. It was the homeworld of a large sentient species of carnivorous plant. It was also home to other organisms including magnetic rock chimps, a five-eyed bird, and centipedes.
